A one-stop service for Cal students to be connected to any resource, program, or opportunity at UC Berkeley

Just fill out the form to get connected!

The Process

You submit the Connect@Cal form with a question, request, or issue
We search through our centralized database, work with our partners, and compile a response
You get connected to the most relevant resources and head on to a brighter future!

Our Mission

We believe that the overabundance of information, siloed resources, and the state of UC Berkeley's support system have inhibited students from achieving holistic wellness on campus. Connect@Cal serves as UC Berkeley’s trusted resource hub, connecting students to the most relevant resources and opportunities with a simple form submission
image

Our Vision

We believe that the overabundance of information, siloed resources, and the state of UC Berkeley's support system have inhibited students from achieving holistic wellness on campus. Connect@Cal serves as UC Berkeley’s trusted resource hub, connecting students to the most relevant resources and opportunities with a simple form submission
